---
title: Sweet Mustard Crumbed Haloumi with Roasted Veggies & Pesto Dressing
description: Take a winter veggie toss to new heights with this tumble of baby spinach, rocket and roasted veggies. As a special topping, we’ve coated haloumi in a mild sweet mustard spice mix and fried it for a golden finish. Add a drizzle of creamy pesto and you’ll be begging for this for dinner every night!
